心機讀書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:40:52.000Z","msg":"thx ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實PPP 3個theme 要讀咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽人講housing 好似好D 真？？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T17:41:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nhousing 同另外2個嘅分別在於grad 左係有專業認證 (HKIH)，<br />\n搵物管係易D，但要睇你係咪想行物管狗條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外2個我唔太熟，大概係Public Mgt = 公共管理，要讀下Organizational Behaviour/ HR/ finance resource mgt 嗰D；<br />\nPolitic 就好明顯啦=政治<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16fdba28d19bdb97fcd29944d5cee35c99e9152b","tid":2149612,"uid":353313,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T18:15:42.000Z","msg":"我2019entry 讀咗一個sem就quit左 <br />\n今年取消咗考試 每科都要交幾份3.4000字paper代替<br />\n第一個sem political science, urban studies, management <br />\n如果冇興趣真係好悶 同埋有大量專有知識要學<br />\n勁多paper (1000字起跳) presentation <br />\n唔鍾意睇文嘅 或者英文程度差 係好吃力 <br />\n<br />\nYear2 可以揀 politics,housing, public management <br />\nintern 方面 選擇非常少 （議員助理辦事處,ngo, 房屋署,hk police force) , 2000幾蚊返朝九晚五 返足兩個月 <br />\n<br />\nBusiness college Case competition 一律冇機會玩 連mass email都唔會send俾你 畢咗業出嚟都唔知做咩<br />\n<br />\n身邊有好多asso上黎 大陸人都好多  身邊好多朋友都轉科 <br />\n算係容易過3 不過workload 我個人覺得算大 <br />\nPolitical science 我個人覺得 如果唔擅長諗嘢 呢科好容易爛 利申: D爛咗 <br />\n其他course都比較易讀 但係難攞高分"},{"pid":"ee600ce2ae06e10992deddac9826f28cdb2ada9d","tid":2149612,"uid":353313,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3c0c1cd28abc4e0c99809c203bb5c7a50eea3b8b","tid":2149612,"uid":142706,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"0b230b7100f7ce0e4699db80e2f193c2943fc250","tid":2149612,"uid":310127,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c19fb37fa851e1ad96fe9035c04962e0